<body>
	<div id="flex">
		<header>
			<h1><a href="/">Otherside for Twitter</a></h1>
			<p>Otherside creates a <a href="https://twitter.com/lists">Twitter List</a> of the accounts someone follows, letting you to see Twitter from their perspective.</p>
		</header>
		<main>
			<%= yield %>
			<ul>
				<div>Limitations</div>
				<li>Lists can only contain up to 5,000 accounts.</li>
